election_record.label: Connecticut 1820 Electoral College

overview.note: Samuel H. Phillips received 69 votes as Samuel Phillips, 51 votes as Samuel W. Phillips, 1 vote as Samuel R. Phillips, 3 votes as Samuel Wphillip and 42 votes as Samuel H. Phelps.
Isaiah Loomis received 56 votes as Israel Loomis, 15 votes as Isaac Loomis, 65 votes as Josiah Loomis and 13 votes as Isaiah Loomis, 2nd.
John Alsop received 2 votes as John Alsoph and 2 votes as John Asoph.
Asa Bacon received 12 votes as Asa Bacon, Jr.
William M. Betts received 1 vote as William Betts.
Epaphroditus Chapman received 1 vote as Epaphroditus Champion, Jr.
John T. Peters received 5 votes as John S. Peters.
Nathaniel Terry received 5 votes as Nathaniel Perry.
Thomas S. Williams received 1 vote as Thomas Williams.
John B. Watrous received 1 vote as John B. Watross.
David Daggett received 1 vote as David D. Dagget.
Samuel W. Dana received 1 vote as Samuel Dana.
Samuel B. Sherwood received 1 vote as Samuel R. Sherwood.
Nathaniel Smith received 1 vote as Nathan Smith.
